  return [200, userDB.users];
});
Mock.onGet('/api/user').reply(function (config) {
  var id = config.data;
  var response = userDB.users.find(function (user) {
    return user.id === id;
  });
  return [200, response];
});
Mock.onPost('/api/user/delete').reply(function (config) {
  var user = JSON.parse(config.data);
  var index = {
    i: 0
  };
  userDB.users.forEach(function (element) {
    if (element.id === user.id) {
      return [200, userDB.users.splice(index.i, 1)];
    }

    index.i++;
  });
  return [200, userDB.users];
});
Mock.onPost('/api/user/update').reply(function (config) {
  var user = JSON.parse(config.data);
  var index = {
    i: 0
  };
  userDB.users.forEach(function (element) {
    if (element.id === user.id) {
      userDB.users[index.i] = user;
      return [200, userDB.users];
    }

    index.i++;
  });
  return [200, userDB.users];
});
Mock.onPost('/api/user/add').reply(function (config) {
  var user = JSON.parse(config.data);
  userDB.users.push(user);
  return [200, userDB.users];
});

Mock.onGet('/api/user/all').reply((config) => {
    return [200, userDB.users]
})

Mock.onGet('/api/user').reply((config) => {
    const id = config.data
    const response = userDB.users.find((user) => user.id === id)
    return [200, response]
})

Mock.onPost('/api/user/delete').reply((config) => {
    let user = JSON.parse(config.data)
    let index = { i: 0 }
    userDB.users.forEach((element) => {
        if (element.id === user.id) {
            return [200, userDB.users.splice(index.i, 1)]
        }
        index.i++
    })
    return [200, userDB.users]
})

Mock.onPost('/api/user/update').reply((config) => {
    let user = JSON.parse(config.data)
    let index = { i: 0 }
    userDB.users.forEach((element) => {
        if (element.id === user.id) {
            userDB.users[index.i] = user
            return [200, userDB.users]
        }
        index.i++
    })
    return [200, userDB.users]
})

Mock.onPost('/api/user/add').reply((config) => {
    let user = JSON.parse(config.data)
    userDB.users.push(user)
    return [200, userDB.users]
})
